Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:04.35,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\pos(1150,170)}第9話{\fs20}\N\N{\fs70\fsp0}晚宴上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,主張自己是第四身份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為了達成目的就去無差別恐怖攻擊的團體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,第四身份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在叫利貝爾的城市裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,暗中流通被稱為「魔藥」的可疑藥品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟桃子應教會的西西莉雅司祭的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,開始了這件事的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子從偶然遇到的亞修娜公主處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了魔藥生產據點的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.31,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,另一方面 我也開始行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,調查這裡的第四身份代表人物 瑪儂·利貝爾的周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我潛入了她主辦的晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知為何 也帶上了這一大累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是個純潔正直 而且強大的神官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你們玩得開心 我是個純潔正直 且強大的神官哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,給二位獻上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里 我應該和你說過不要太顯眼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.12,0:01:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這是晚宴呢 要是不跟陌生人打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是更奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊 要是誰叫你去哪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你千萬別跟著去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 食物和飲料也不能碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道裡面放了什麼奇怪的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 我都聽你說好幾遍了 沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙 你這是把我當什麼人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 應該是心理年齡只有10歲的傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才還有兩個穿著高貴的阿姨誇我說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,「真是很棒的淑女啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我是位傑出的淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是擔心你這點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 心思也不能一直放在燈里身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里 我要離開一會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎 人家好寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是淑女就不要撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要乖乖等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮沒出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有聖女瑪爾塔的加護啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,神官來這裡做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對魔藥的生產據點來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這守衛還真是不稱職啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 趕緊完事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,去看前輩的禮服裝扮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要找的東西是瑪儂·利貝爾生產並流通魔藥的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你這消除氣息的技巧真高明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是掩人耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而是讓人看到也不會意識到的隱形嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真是自然得差點我都沒發現你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到 居然還有人跟我一樣趁著晚宴潛入城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪儂·利貝爾還真是樹敵不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是古里札力卡王國的公主騎士 亞修娜·古里札力卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你又是何方神聖？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我家有個工作時間出來偷情的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來提醒她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這在扮演貴族大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,第二身份的淑女可不會這種隱形的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 殿下發現了我的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那就也不是第二身份的淑女了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,騎士階級跟他們不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在保持可愛的同時還得變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說你也是這種類型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多可以把頭轉過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞到不敢示人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我這等不入流的角色 能請您當做沒看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我看到可疑的人就想砍上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且從你的舉止來看 應該是高手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要親眼見識見識別人的強大之處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說要我和殿下戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,理解得這麼快真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,導力槍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,按理說應該是違禁品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,列車上的恐怖分子也是 到底是從哪得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,別…別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,以你們的導力 即使開槍也會被我的壁障彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 能告訴我帳本在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還有魔藥的生成導器 我要記錄到教典裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要是說謊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是什麼下場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有興趣戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可要好好享受這場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我先發制人卻被後手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很不錯的導力操作技術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人 導力的量並不怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人果然很無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,魔導構築的氣息 大的要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,泡泡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,用泡泡遮擋視線的同時自由地操縱短劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,多麼流暢的導力操作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,被手下留情也好 被隨意擺布也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,都很久沒有過了 我太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要加倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是用強硬的手段也要瞻仰一下你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,否則我可咽不下這口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,技術上比不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就用我的優勢來取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼 著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是瑪瑙去的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.75,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,被算計了 我居然如此任人擺布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,除了前輩 全部去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 她就是「前輩」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今天晚上見到桃子的時候能用這個來捉弄她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪 這絕對很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那個時候感受到的違和感逐漸變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,重複了很多次的「回歸」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要說在利貝爾發生的大事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有被送進霧魔殿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這一次 有太多之前沒有經歷的事情發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在市場被襲擊 召開晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還有剛才看到的那個火柱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,之前一次都沒有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很大的火柱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 兩個人都很理性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有引起很大的損害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我這麼突然真是太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫瑪儂·利貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你是第一次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,之前也沒有發生過 被這個人搭話這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 給別人添麻煩也要有個限度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,和傳聞一樣是個戰鬥狂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因為剛才的騷動 第四身份應該加強了警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很可惜 但今天還是撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快和燈里匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你很在意我是什麼人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,請不用在意 我只是個代行者罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,單純只是想見你一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的母親也有同你一樣的黑髮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話能跟我說說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,關於你來這之前所在之地的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是來自日本的異世界人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我基本失去了 過往16年在日本的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 原來你已經使用力量到那種程度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此我也很羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你擁有我想擁有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,能隨自己意志改變世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很失禮 但如果你能離開這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,還請你務必自由地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,原本該發生的事出現如此大的改變的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那所謂知曉未來的我擁有的優勢就被瓦解了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,明明這次已經到了不救瑪瑙不行的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦怎麼辦怎麼辦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怕 她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 我要冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這說不定是個好變化
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,總而言之 我得先找到產生巨大變化的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 我得調查剛才那個好像知道什麼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先從她開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,燈里真是的 我都跟她說那麼多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 根據帳本記錄來看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,魔藥的生產是從兩週前開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前都很安分的瑪儂·利貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,突然起頭從外面運來了魔藥生成導器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,兩週前到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這個房間的結構
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺有原罪概念儀式場的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 中間應該有一座靈柩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是靈柩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,鐵處女？拷問器具…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 這就是魔藥的生成導器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真是惡趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,居然利用這麼小的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然可能已經沒救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然不是在打開鐵處女的時候發動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在拯救孩子的時候發動的條件啟動式魔導
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且這根刺…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然還塗了毒嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,設計這個陷阱的人 性格真是太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,至少得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她和瑪儂·利貝爾小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是問剛才那位很可愛的神官小姐對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他們是說過話的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 好像並沒有聊很久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非她被瑪儂小姐帶走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好像不是那樣的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對 還看到她後面一個人待著的時候一直喊怎麼辦怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不是被拐走的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:17.06,Top,,0,0,0,,雖然長得很可愛 卻是個很有個性的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,桃子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那個陷阱發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,終於要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的復仇實現之日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼都不用說 桃子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,根據你從教典傳來的紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經知道發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看到有個孩子 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 你做得很好了 桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我感到自豪的後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 之後交給我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,該死的第四身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,中的毒很深 情況並不是很理想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 多虧她體內有大量導力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,毒素的蔓延很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,應該還有救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 非常感謝教會迅速有效的搭救 西西莉雅司祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用不著感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,保護神官是第一身份的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那燈里小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我認為她多半是出於好奇心在利貝爾城堡裡逛 然後迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也有可能被第四身份抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那群人好像對她沒什麼想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以西西莉雅司祭 能封鎖整個利貝爾城堡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,根據桃子發過來的影像記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,第四身份很明顯與魔藥的生產逃不開關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,將那些以利貝爾為據點的第四身份全部消滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我會潛入城堡抓住瑪儂·利貝爾和主要成員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,同時保護好燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,您能向騎士階級請求協助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然會找別人幫忙 和陽炎不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,西西莉雅司祭認識導師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我被她當著面說無能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,但你記不得我了也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.57,0:20:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,另外瑪瑙 你就不懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,懷疑我與這次的事情有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話我懷疑過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟歐威爾大司教的事情才過去沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是與您接觸後 我選擇了相信您並提出了那樣的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,西西莉雅司祭 請您協助我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我去和騎士階級說這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,利貝爾島從今天中午開始封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,躲藏在島內的第四身份 以及製造和販賣魔藥的人都將被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,奉勸你們即刻認罪伏誅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,利貝爾島從今天中午開始封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:04.52,Top,,0,0,0,,躲藏在島內的第四身份 以及製造和販賣魔藥的人都將被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到他們的動作這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別慌 我們還沒被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這下難辦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先讓那些人閉嘴比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,被誰碰過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始討論對策
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 居然能做到這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,潛入到我房間裡的人就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪儂小姐 幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事情想問你 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎你 燈里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 迷途人的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:32.99,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Laykarf dunon a hethkka ja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.28,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dullun katre n’a sol solle flare-esta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.53,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sae que ja ton tonnu hanja
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:38.66,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ju va lerhen n’a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:53.21,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Loop through a silky ribbon, my pretender
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.68,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hide a scarlet letter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.43,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manuals in hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:01.51,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We paint the world a bit redder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:06.56,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bury my new friend, means to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.90,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Decomposing sailor shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.15,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Button down jackets, pleated skirts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.90,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.61,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In the mirror I am cinderella
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.70,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Too late to reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:26.50,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If the future needs a billion samples of flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.71,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’m your reaper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.96,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I’ve no colour
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:35.88,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So the least I can do for you is endure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.01,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We walked down the aisle unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:44.81,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We walked down the aisle unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.39,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Remaining strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.94,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Laykarf dunon a hethkka ja
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.07,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dullun katre n’a sol solle flare-esta
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:54.44,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sae que ja ton tonnu hanja
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.44,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ju va lerhen n’a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:53.21,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的冒牌貨繫上絲帶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.68,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}藏起深紅的信箋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:58.43,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿起教典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:01.51,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們把世界塗得更紅一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:06.56,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}埋葬我的新朋友 讓一切結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.90,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}解開水手服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.15,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脫下襯衫 褪去百褶裙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.90,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穿上盛裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.61,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在鏡子裡我是灰姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.70,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而為時已晚 已無法重生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:26.50,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果未來需要十億朵鮮花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.71,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我是你的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.96,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我失去了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:35.88,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能為你忍受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.01,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走在無人踏足的側堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:44.81,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走在無人踏足的側堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.39,OP_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永遠不得相識
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:20.32,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}静かな夢の中を　彷徨っていたあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:30.79,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君と出会えたことで　何かが弾けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:36.08,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何かが動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:41.97,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}軋む空の青を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:51.02,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この想い伝えたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.23,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今この瞬間を　焼き付けるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:07.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重ね合う手と手が　いつか離れる時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君が変えてくれた　色付く世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}共鳴する心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:25.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}だから詠うよ　この声が続く限り
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:31.77,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君に届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:20.32,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}那天我彷徨在寂靜的夢境中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:30.79,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}與你相遇後夢境驚起了漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:36.08,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}掀起了波瀾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:41.97,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一道聲音跨過藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.97,0:22:51.02,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}傳達這份念想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.23,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}於此刻開始燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:07.07,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直到緊扣的雙手分開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.62,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我的世界因你塗抹上了色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.83,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}正因為我們心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:25.93,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}所以我才要一直歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:31.77,ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直到傳達給你
